name: Shimano Ultegra CS-6700 10 Speed 11-25T Cassette
description: This cassette from the Ultegra series provides smooth, lightning quick shifting.Alloy sprocket carrier keeps the cogs in check when shifting under load.Sprockets have a nickel-plated finish.Compatible with super narrow HG 10-speed chains.Sprocket sizes: 11-12-13-14-15-17-19-21-23-25.
